{
  "stem": "9723.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after a month or so, the unit moved out, started going west, following the front by about 20, 30 miles.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Wind out-- uh, wound up uh, by Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We stayed on the other side of the river while Warsaw was besieged.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There is a long story about what happened in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nobody could understand why didn't we just go in and take Warsaw?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it so happened the Polish underground was very right-wing-oriented.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the Russians wanted to make sure that none of these people survived.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they just waited until the Germans killed all of them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then they finally took Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So uh, we were sitting there for several months, doing nothing, just perhaps shooting rifles across the river, just killing time.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Eventually we went to Warsaw, took Warsaw, and started going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Went to Germany.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I wound up in Berlin about one or two days after Berlin was taken.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Stayed in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When was that?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was uh, May, I believe, in 1945.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So then the war was over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We went back and uh, we stationed near Warsaw for a short time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then I was discharged.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had enough army life, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they let me go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After all, I [? was ?] underage.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So uh, they [? sent ?] a document, being discharged to uh, continue his studies.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You said that you-- you were in charge of the radio and you learned the Morse code?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I wasn't in charge, but uh--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A little bit, yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were two cases in our unit where people got badly wounded.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And uh, it just so happened, I guess, during battle, you can't really predict what's going to be where.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
